  <entry>
    <title>欧几里得算法</title>
    <link href="/2024/12/22/%E6%AC%A7%E5%87%A0%E9%87%8C%E5%BE%97%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95/"/>
    <url>/2024/12/22/%E6%AC%A7%E5%87%A0%E9%87%8C%E5%BE%97%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="欧几里得算法（gcd）"><a href="#欧几里得算法（gcd）" class="headerlink" title="欧几里得算法（gcd）"></a>欧几里得算法（gcd）</h2><p>对于整数 $a$ 和 $b$，$\gcd(a, b)$ 表示 $a$ 和 $b$ 的最大公约数。例如，$\gcd(12, 18) &#x3D; 6$，因为 $6$ 是 $12$ 和 $18$ 的最大公因数。</p><p>欧几里得算法（Euclidean algorithm），又称<strong>辗转相除法</strong>，可以高效地计算两个整数的最大公约数，其核心原理是：</p><p>$$\gcd(a, b) &#x3D; \gcd(b, a \bmod b)$$</p><h2 id="原理推导"><a href="#原理推导" class="headerlink" title="原理推导"></a>原理推导</h2><p>设 $a &gt; b$，由带余除法，可以将 $a$ 表示为：</p><p>$$a &#x3D; k \cdot b + r, \quad 0 \le r &lt; b$$</p><p>其中 $k &#x3D; \lfloor a &#x2F; b \rfloor$，$r &#x3D; a \bmod b$。</p><p>现在令 $d &#x3D; \gcd(a, b)$，即 $d \mid a$ 且 $d \mid b$。由 $r &#x3D; a - k \cdot b$ 可知，$d$ 也能整除 $r$，因此 $d$ 是 $b$ 和 $r$ 的公因数，即 $\gcd(a, b) \le \gcd(b, r)$。</p><p>反过来，设 $d’ &#x3D; \gcd(b, r)$，则 $d’ \mid b$ 且 $d’ \mid r$。由 $a &#x3D; k \cdot b + r$ 可知，$d’$ 也能整除 $a$，因此 $d’$ 是 $a$ 和 $b$ 的公因数，即 $\gcd(b, r) \le \gcd(a, b)$。</p><p>综上，$\gcd(a, b) &#x3D; \gcd(b, r) &#x3D; \gcd(b, a \bmod b)$。证毕。</p><p>这个过程的妙处在于：每次递归都将问题规模缩小，且余数 $r$ 必然会不断减小，最终收敛到 $0$。当余数为 $0$ 时，除数即为答案。</p><h2 id="算法实现"><a href="#算法实现" class="headerlink" title="算法实现"></a>算法实现</h2><h3 id="递归版本"><a href="#递归版本" class="headerlink" title="递归版本"></a>递归版本</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">gcd</span>(<span class="hljs-params">a: <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span>, b: <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span>) -&gt; <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span>:<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> b == <span class="hljs-number">0</span>:<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> a<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> gcd(b, a % b)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="迭代版本"><a href="#迭代版本" class="headerlink" title="迭代版本"></a>迭代版本</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">gcd_iter</span>(<span class="hljs-params">a: <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span>, b: <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span>) -&gt; <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span>:<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> b != <span class="hljs-number">0</span>:<br>        a, b = b, a % b<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> a<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="C-实现"><a href="#C-实现" class="headerlink" title="C++ 实现"></a>C++ 实现</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">gcd</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> a, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> b)</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (b) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> tmp = a % b;<br>        a = b;<br>        b = tmp;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> a;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>C++17 起，标准库中已内置 <code>std::gcd(a, b)</code>，位于 <code>&lt;numeric&gt;</code> 头文件中。</p><h2 id="手动演算示例"><a href="#手动演算示例" class="headerlink" title="手动演算示例"></a>手动演算示例</h2><p>以 $\gcd(252, 105)$ 为例：</p><table><thead><tr><th>步骤</th><th>a</th><th>b</th><th>a mod b</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td>252</td><td>105</td><td>42</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>105</td><td>42</td><td>21</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td>42</td><td>21</td><td>0</td></tr></tbody></table><p>余数为 $0$ 时，$b &#x3D; 21$，故 $\gcd(252, 105) &#x3D; 21$。</p><h2 id="时间复杂度"><a href="#时间复杂度" class="headerlink" title="时间复杂度"></a>时间复杂度</h2><p>设 $a &gt; b$，欧几里得算法的时间复杂度为 $O(\log \min(a, b))$。</p><p>粗略分析：每两次迭代，较大的数至少减半（因为 $r &lt; b$ 且 $a \bmod b &lt; a&#x2F;2$ 当 $b \le a&#x2F;2$ 时显然，否则两轮后也会减半），因此迭代次数不超过 $2 \log_2(\min(a, b))$。</p><p>更精确地说，最坏情况发生在相邻两个斐波那契数上：$\gcd(F_{n+1}, F_n)$ 需要约 $n$ 次取模运算，因此迭代次数上界为 $O(\log_\varphi \min(a, b))$，其中 $\varphi &#x3D; \frac{1+\sqrt{5}}{2}$（黄金比例）。</p><h2 id="扩展欧几里得算法"><a href="#扩展欧几里得算法" class="headerlink" title="扩展欧几里得算法"></a>扩展欧几里得算法</h2><p>扩展欧几里得算法不仅能求 $\gcd(a, b)$，还能找到整数 $x, y$，使得：</p><p>$$a \cdot x + b \cdot y &#x3D; \gcd(a, b)$$</p><p>这个等式称为<strong>贝祖等式</strong>（Bézout’s identity）。</p><h3 id="推导思路"><a href="#推导思路" class="headerlink" title="推导思路"></a>推导思路</h3><p>在辗转相除的过程中，维护系数 $x, y$。设当前步骤有：</p><ul><li>$a &#x3D; q \cdot b + r$</li><li>且我们知道 $\gcd(b, r) &#x3D; b \cdot x’ + r \cdot y’$</li></ul><p>代入 $r &#x3D; a - q \cdot b$：</p><p>$$\gcd &#x3D; b \cdot x’ + (a - q \cdot b) \cdot y’ &#x3D; a \cdot y’ + b \cdot (x’ - q \cdot y’)$$</p><p>因此系数更新为：$x &#x3D; y’, ; y &#x3D; x’ - q \cdot y’$。</p><h3 id="实现"><a href="#实现" class="headerlink" title="实现"></a>实现</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">exgcd</span>(<span class="hljs-params">a: <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span>, b: <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span>):<br>    <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-string">    返回 (gcd, x, y)，满足 a*x + b*y = gcd(a, b)</span><br><span class="hljs-string">    &quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> b == <span class="hljs-number">0</span>:<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> a, <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span><br>    d, x1, y1 = exgcd(b, a % b)<br>    x = y1<br>    y = x1 - (a // b) * y1<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> d, x, y<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>迭代版：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">exgcd_iter</span>(<span class="hljs-params">a: <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span>, b: <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span>):<br>    x0, x1 = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span><br>    y0, y1 = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> b:<br>        q = a // b<br>        a, b = b, a % b<br>        x0, x1 = x1, x0 - q * x1<br>        y0, y1 = y1, y0 - q * y1<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> a, x0, y0<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="典型应用"><a href="#典型应用" class="headerlink" title="典型应用"></a>典型应用</h2><h3 id="1-求乘法逆元"><a href="#1-求乘法逆元" class="headerlink" title="1. 求乘法逆元"></a>1. 求乘法逆元</h3><p>在模 $m$ 意义下，若 $\gcd(a, m) &#x3D; 1$，则可通过扩展欧几里得算法求 $a$ 的逆元：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">mod_inv</span>(<span class="hljs-params">a: <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span>, m: <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span>) -&gt; <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span>:<br>    d, x, _ = exgcd(a, m)<br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># d == gcd(a, m)，互质时 d = 1</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> x % m<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>因为 $a \cdot x + m \cdot y &#x3D; 1 \implies a \cdot x \equiv 1 \pmod{m}$，所以 $x$ 就是 $a$ 模 $m$ 下的逆元。</p><h3 id="2-求解线性丢番图方程"><a href="#2-求解线性丢番图方程" class="headerlink" title="2. 求解线性丢番图方程"></a>2. 求解线性丢番图方程</h3><p>方程 $a x + b y &#x3D; c$ 有整数解的充要条件是 $\gcd(a, b) \mid c$。先用扩展欧几里得求出一组特解 $(x_0, y_0)$，通解为：</p><p>$$\begin{cases} x &#x3D; x_0 + \dfrac{b}{d} \cdot t \[8pt] y &#x3D; y_0 - \dfrac{a}{d} \cdot t \end{cases}, \quad t \in \mathbb{Z}, \quad d &#x3D; \gcd(a, b)$$</p><h3 id="3-最小公倍数"><a href="#3-最小公倍数" class="headerlink" title="3. 最小公倍数"></a>3. 最小公倍数</h3><p>利用 $\gcd(a, b) \cdot \operatorname{lcm}(a, b) &#x3D; |a \cdot b|$：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">lcm</span>(<span class="hljs-params">a: <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span>, b: <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span>) -&gt; <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span>:<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> a // gcd(a, b) * b  <span class="hljs-comment"># 先除后乘，防止溢出</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
